trans-unit.source:
\n

Defines the standard keywords that apply to events.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxxxxxx xxx xxxxxxxx xxxxxxxx xxxx xxxxx xx xxxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

All the bits are set to 1, representing every possible group of events.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxx xxx xxxx xxx xxx xx 0$ xxxxxxxxxxxx xxxxx xxxxxxxx xxxxx xx xxxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

Attached to all failed security audit events.
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxxxxxxx xx xxx xxxxxx xxxxxxxx xxxxx xxxxxx.

trans-unit.source:
Use this keyword only for events in the security log.

\n
trans-unit.target: Xxx xxxx xxxxxxx xxxx xxx xxxxxx xx xxx xxxxxxxx xxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

Attached to all successful security audit events.
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxxxxxxx xx xxx xxxxxxxxxx xxxxxxxx xxxxx xxxxxx.

trans-unit.source:
Use this keyword only for events in the security log.

\n
trans-unit.target: Xxx xxxx xxxxxxx xxxx xxx xxxxxx xx xxx xxxxxxxx xxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

Attached to transfer events where the related activity ID (correlation ID) is a computed value and is not guaranteed to be unique (that is, it is not a real GUID).

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxxxxxxx xx xxxxxxxx xxxxxx xxxxx xxx xxxxxxx xxxxxxxx XX $xxxxxxxxxxx XX$ xx x xxxxxxxx xxxxx xxx xx xxx xxxxxxxxxx xx xx xxxxxx $xxxx xx$ xx xx xxx x xxxx XXXX$.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

Attached to events that are raised by using the RaiseEvent function.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxxxxxxx xx xxxxxx xxxx xxx xxxxxx xx xxxxx xxx $xxxxxx$XxxxxXxxxx$$xxxxxx$ xxxxxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

No filtering on keywords is performed when the event is published.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xx xxxxxxxxx xx xxxxxxxx xx xxxxxxxxx xxxx xxx xxxxx xx xxxxxxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

Attached to all Service Quality Mechanism (SQM) events.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxxxxxxx xx xxx Xxxxxxx Xxxxxxx Xxxxxxxxx $XXX$ xxxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

Attached to all Windows Diagnostics Infrastructure (WDI) context events.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxxxxxxx xx xxx Xxxxxxx Xxxxxxxxxxx Xxxxxxxxxxxxxx $XXX$ xxxxxxx xxxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

Attached to all Windows Diagnostics Infrastructure (WDI) diagnostic events.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxxxxxxx xx xxx Xxxxxxx Xxxxxxxxxxx Xxxxxxxxxxxxxx $XXX$ xxxxxxxxxx xxxxxx.$$x$$x
